## Overview

This talk is going to be all about modules and imports.

This is all stuff that's good to know as a typescript developer.
However, a lot of this talk will be about things other than typescript,
such as your browser and Node.js.

This week: CommonJS and ECMAScript Modules
Next week: Packages, package.json, and package managers

## To follow along:

These are all runnable examples. I encourage you to check out this repository and try them yourself!

```
git clone https://github.com/nickretallack/typescript-talk.git
cd typescript-talk
corepack enable pnpm
pnpm install
```

These instructions assume you already have `git`, `node`, and `corepack`.

